de.amr.plt.rcParkingRobot

Class IAndroidHmi.ParkingSlot

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.amr.plt.rcParkingRobot.IAndroidHmi.ParkingSlot
  • Enclosing interface:
    IAndroidHmi

    public static class IAndroidHmi.ParkingSlot
extends java.lang.Object
    ParkingSlot re-implementation for Android. This class has the same functionality as ParkingSlot from INavigation.java but uses only Android classes. This is necessary because e.g. lejos.geom.Point is not available on Android. Contains all necessary information about one parking slot. This is the slot status (whether it is/is not satisfying or has to be scanned again), its ID, the position of the slot begin front boundary and the position of the slot back boundary.
    Author:
    PLT

    • Field Detail

      • ID

        int ID
        stores the parking slot ID that is the number of recent detected parking spaces incremented by one. When delegating the robot to a special parking slot a distinction between the spaces is necessary and given by identification.
